Author: _t1nk_
Text: Yes. I feel so guilty and ashamed and I just need to have any and all evidence completely gone so I don't get found out and also so I don't make it worse. But then whenever the "so full I am sick and want to die" feeling has passed and I want to binge again I feel even guiltier at the idea of spending money and over all the *food* (because is that junk really food?) I wasted. Ugh.  I have been trying to just keep reminding myself this so I don't actually binge.
